core.tut.pori.http.parameters

Class DataGroups

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.parameters.HTTPParameter
      • core.tut.pori.http.parameters.DataGroups

  • public final class DataGroups
extends HTTPParameter
    Default dataGroups parser. Syntax: ?data_groups=DATA_GROUP_VALUE or with type ?data_groups=TYPE;DATA_GROUP_VALUE, these can be combined: ?data_groups=DATA_GROUP_VALUE,TYPE:DATA_GROUP_VALUE Note: this has no way of knowing if the given string are valid for the required context, you should check the values manually There is no concept of order for the data groups, and they can be provided in any order for the data_groups parameter.
